    {
      "start": 215.78,
      "end": 216.08,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.2,
      "end": 217.06,
      "text": "An IT executive."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.36,
      "end": 220.38,
      "text": "진짜 professional 하는 워커인 것 같은 느낌이 들었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.38,
      "end": 224.2,
      "text": "I'm from Silicon Valley, California, the IT capital of the world."
    },
    {
      "start": 224.34,
      "end": 224.62,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 224.62,
      "end": 230.38,
      "text": "Many people work in that field, and he seemed like the perfect actor to play this part."
    },
    {
      "start": 230.46,
      "end": 231.18,
      "text": "Oh, 그렇구나."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.3,
