      "text": "He's played many, many roles, leading and supporting roles in famous Hollywood films."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.3,
      "end": 261.94,
      "text": "그렇군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 262.32,
      "end": 269.52,
      "text": "그리고, it was not the first time, Kate Blanchett하고 같이 일을 한 게 이게 처음이 아니래요, 이 영화가."
    },
    {
