      "text": "Okay, so they had experience on screen together, which made this performance maybe a little more natural."
    },
    {
      "start": 288.26,
      "end": 288.7,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 289.24,
      "end": 291.08,
      "text": "분명히 영향이 있을 거라고 생각합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.56,
      "end": 292.82,
      "text": "오늘 장면 먼저 듣고 올게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.38,
      "end": 295.42,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm just anxious about the Trump."
