      "text": "I don't know."
    },
    {
      "start": 316.05,
      "end": 319.75,
      "text": "I think maybe we need to revisit this idea of finding someone for you to talk to."
    },
    {
      "start": 320.51,
      "end": 323.67,
      "text": "네, 이번엔 부부의 대화였습니다 in the restaurant."
    },
    {
      "start": 323.77,
